bio:
Henry is a Malaysian Google Developer Expert in Web Technologies. He is currently working as a frontend engineer in Hamburg, Germany.

He loves to learn, experiment and share all the cool stuffs like Progressive Web Apps, Chrome DevToosl, Project Fugu (Web Capabilities), Firebase, and more.
